snippet.title: Assault Bots Gameplay Walkthrough (Android, iOS) - Part 1
snippet.description:
Assault Bots Gameplay Walkthrough (Android, iOS) - Part 1
Assault Bots is now available on Android and ios, you can download through Google Playstore and iOS through Appstore.

------------------------------------------
▬▬▬ Description ▬▬▬
------------------------------------------
Multiplayer robot shooter

Customize your vehicle, and play against other players in an online robot vehicle shooter. Choose from wheels, mech legs, helicopter blades, and customize your robot in many different ways. Pick the alien team or human AI team and destroy the other team in online multiplayer. You can use machine guns, lasers, all different types of weapons and add-ons to make your bot the best.

There is also an offline mode where you can play against bots, in singleplayer.
------------------------------------------
▬▬▬ Download Links ▬▬▬
------------------------------------------
iOS ►►https://testflight.apple.com/join/DoWqqxYC
Android ►►https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.BlayzeGames.Lucas_New_Game
